prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "The system waits for a customer.",
      "evidence_quote": "The system starts by waiting for a customer."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "When a customer begins a purchase, items are added one by one.",
      "evidence_quote": "When a customer begins a purchase, items are added one by one. The user can keep adding items until they finish."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The system waits for payment after all items are added.",
      "evidence_quote": "Once all items are added, the system waits for payment."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "After the payment is made, the system goes back to waiting for the next customer.",
      "evidence_quote": "After the payment is made, the system goes back to waiting for the next customer."
    }
  ]
}

llm_response:
```json
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "The system waits for a customer.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall wait for a customer."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "When a customer begins a purchase, items are added one by one.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall add items one by one when a customer begins a purchase."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The system waits for payment after all items are added.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall wait for payment after all items are added."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "After the payment is made, the system goes back to waiting for the next customer.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall go back to waiting for the next customer after the payment is made."
    }
  ]
}
```
